if(boolean condition) {
//does this part ONLY if the boolean condition is true.

Nesting if statement
-putting if statement inside if.
if(i > 0){
    if(i < 20){
        System.out.println("...");

else if statement
int i = 0 {
    //you can put System.out.println here
    } else if(i < 0){
    //can be System.out.println
    } else {
    //System.out.println here;
    }
-can have if inside else if or if statement.
-ladder is sequential so only run if previous statement is FALSE.

-must use == instead of =